metadata.name: Seeing My Life
metadata.description: The following piece means my life, my goals, my drawing talent, my activities and sports, my aspirations, my favorite games, some of my favorite foods, all this I have captured in an abstract art, the eye in the middle means the visualization of my life at my 12 years old, this drawing started as an idea but with effort and dedication I turned it into an art, this way I want you to know better how I am beyond the artist.
